{
  "text": "In view of the late clinical stage of RSCC at first presentation, with poor median survival times of 10 months or less, as well as the lack of effective adjuvant radiotherapy or chemotherapy, radical resection with clear margins may be the only method to prolong survival. [CITATION_1] ",
